{
  "stem": "20580.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Chetner. ?] And my brother, they take-- one takes him in the corner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he says to him, over here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He took out $200.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He had boots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He put the $200.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He says, just try to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You've got everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had leather.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had needles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I had cotton.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And since today, I put-- always I have cotton with me with a needle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Till today on, I had always, you see, [LAUGHS] with me a cotton with needle over here, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because it reminds me that stuff-- anything, a button falls off, I've got right away with me a cotton and a needle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took away all the things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they changed the money-- and they count the money, $30, $40, $10 bills-- what?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never-- not dollar bills, so $10, $15.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- and this guy has the $200.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do we do with the Jews?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kill them?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He get me over here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He, he, he knows-- and the guy shares-- and the lady says-- yell, don't kill them in my apartment!",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't want to see-- I don't want to see this, any of this!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says to the husband-- these are strong guys-- he says, stop it, [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bela! ?] And they listened to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought a plan to bring me, like, to the soldiers that they had from the city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tie us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put us in a wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they bring me to the city-- to the place which I had on the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was 12 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One guy-- this guy goes to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this guy, which he took the money, he tied me up over here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He tied me up, my-- I was naked.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
